<Graph ClassName="SOInvoiceEntryExtAddSOLine" Source="#CDATA" IsNew="True" FileType="NewFile">
	<CDATA name="Source"><![CDATA[using System;
using System.Collections;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using PX.Data;
using PX.Objects.AR;
using PX.Objects.CS;

namespace PX.Objects.SO
{
  public class SOInvoiceEntryExtAddSOLine : PXGraphExtension<SOInvoiceEntry>
  {
    public PXSelectJoin<Sel.SOLine,
      InnerJoin<SOOrder, On<SOOrder.orderType, Equal<Sel.SOLine.orderType>, And<SOOrder.orderNbr, Equal<Sel.SOLine.orderNbr>>>,
      InnerJoin<SOOrderType, On<SOOrderType.orderType, Equal<Sel.SOLine.orderType>>>>,
      Where<SOOrder.customerID, Equal<Current<ARInvoice.customerID>>,
      And<SOOrderType.requireShipping, Equal<boolTrue>, And<SOOrderType.aRDocType, NotEqual<ARDocType.noUpdate>,
      And<Sub<Sel.SOLine.baseOrderQty, Sel.SOLine.baseShippedQty>, Greater<decimal0>,
      And<Sel.SOLine.pOCreate, Equal<boolFalse>, And<Sel.SOLine.completed, Equal<boolFalse>>>>>>>,
      OrderBy<Desc<Sel.SOLine.orderNbr>>>
      soLineList;

    public PXAction<ARInvoice> selectSOLine;

	<CDATA name="Source"><![CDATA[using System;
using System.Collections;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Linq;
using PX.Data;
using PX.Objects.AR;
using PX.Objects.CS;
using PX.Objects.IN;

namespace PX.Objects.SO.Ext
{
  public class SOInvoiceEntryExtReturnARTran : PXGraphExtension<SOInvoiceEntry>
  {
    public PXSelectJoin<Sel.ARTran,
      LeftJoin<INTran, On<INTran.aRDocType, Equal<Sel.ARTran.tranType>, And<INTran.aRRefNbr, Equal<Sel.ARTran.refNbr>, And<INTran.aRLineNbr, Equal<Sel.ARTran.lineNbr>>>>>,
      Where<Sel.ARTran.customerID, Equal<Current<ARInvoice.customerID>>, And<Sel.ARTran.released, Equal<boolTrue>,
        And<Where2<Where<INTran.released, Equal<boolTrue>, And<INTran.qty, Greater<decimal0>,
        And<Where<INTran.tranType, Equal<INTranType.issue>, Or<INTran.tranType, Equal<INTranType.debitMemo>, Or<INTran.tranType, Equal<INTranType.invoice>>>>>>>,
        Or<Where<INTran.released, IsNull, And<Where<Sel.ARTran.lineType, Equal<SOLineType.miscCharge>, Or<Sel.ARTran.lineType, Equal<SOLineType.nonInventory>>>>>>>>>>,
        OrderBy<Desc<ARTran.refNbr>>>
      arTranList;

    public PXAction<ARInvoice> selectARTran;
    [PXUIField(DisplayName = "Add Return Line", MapEnableRights = PXCacheRights.Delete, MapViewRights = PXCacheRights.Select)]
    [PXLookupButton]
    public virtual IEnumerable SelectARTran(PXAdapter adapter)
    {
      if (Base.Document.Cache.AllowUpdate)
        arTranList.AskExt();
      return adapter.Get();
    }

    public PXAction<ARInvoice> addARTran;
    [PXUIField(DisplayName = "", MapEnableRights = PXCacheRights.Delete, MapViewRights = PXCacheRights.Select, Visible = false)]
    [PXLookupButton]
    public virtual IEnumerable AddARTran(PXAdapter adapter)
    {
      foreach (Sel.ARTran origTran in arTranList.Cache.Updated)
      {
        if (origTran.Selected != true) continue;

        var tran = (ARTran)Base.Transactions.Cache.CreateInstance();
        tran.InventoryID = origTran.InventoryID;
        tran.SubItemID = origTran.SubItemID;
        tran.SiteID = origTran.SiteID;
        tran.LocationID = origTran.LocationID;
        tran.LotSerialNbr = origTran.LotSerialNbr;
        tran.ExpireDate = origTran.ExpireDate;
        tran.UOM = origTran.UOM;
        tran.Qty = INTranType.InvtMultFromInvoiceType(Base.Document.Current.DocType) * Math.Abs(origTran.Qty ?? 0m);
        tran.CuryUnitPrice = origTran.CuryUnitPrice;
        tran.OrigInvoiceType = origTran.TranType;
        tran.OrigInvoiceNbr = origTran.RefNbr;
        tran.OrigInvoiceLineNbr = origTran.LineNbr;  // not necessary

        Base.InsertInvoiceDirectLine(tran);

        origTran.Selected = false;
      }
      return adapter.Get();
    }

    protected void ARInvoice_RowSelected(PXCache cache, PXRowSelectedEventArgs e)
    {
      var row = (ARInvoice)e.Row;
      selectARTran.SetEnabled(Base.Document.AllowDelete && row != null && row.CustomerID != null);
    }

    protected virtual void _(Events.RowPersisting<Sel.ARTran> e)
    {
      e.Cancel = true;
    }
  }
}]]></CDATA>
